{
  "chapter": 72,
  "chapter_summary": "郭府宴会，项少龙以董匡身份与李园正面交锋。李园先发制人挑惹，项少龙以马喻国，借南北养马之别暗讽楚国耽于逸乐、不谋进取，连消带打令李园哑口无言。席间韩闯透露齐相田单将来邯郸参加合纵密议。赵雅主动向项少龙示好敬酒赔礼，李园随即公然勾搭赵雅，约她共饮，引发郭秀儿负气离席、韩闯嫉妒、赵穆不悦。赵霸谈剑术心得，李园傲慢抢白并以项少龙杀嚣魏牟之事反讽，二人约战后天午后。李园得意宣布已约纪嫣然同游邯郸，项少龙心沉如石。宴会不欢而散，赵穆邀项少龙同车，途中表达对李园的刻骨痛恨，欲借董匡之手挫其气焰。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄今天不惜万水千山，远道来此，只不知是为了什么原因？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 24,
      "line_end": 26
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李兄爱的是美人，董某爱的是骏马。美人到哪里去，李兄追到哪里去，董某则是看哪里的水草肥茂，就往哪儿跑。只要李兄想想自己，当明白董某人的心意。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 32,
      "line_end": 36
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董兄是否暗示我楚国的水草比不上这里？",
      "tone": "冷笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 44,
      "line_end": 46
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李兄想得太远了，鄙人只是打个比喻，其实各处的水草各有优点和缺点，南方气候温和，养马容易，不过养出来的马好看是好看，总不够粗壮，捱不得风寒雨雪；北方养马困难，可是养出来的马刻苦耐劳，发生马瘟的机会亦少多了。所以匈奴人的战马最是著名，正因是苦寒之地，才盛产良马。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 50,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_zong",
      "speaker_name": "郭纵",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "董先生真是句句话不离的把马挂在口边，不愧马痴，来！我们喝一杯。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 90,
      "line_end": 92
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "为韩、楚、赵三国的合纵，我们痛饮一杯！",
      "tone": "豪迈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 96,
      "line_end": 98
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "听说齐王对今天的邯郸之会非常重视，相国田单已亲身赶来，这两天就要到达。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 104
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "董先生！赵雅或有得罪之处，就借这一杯酒作赔礼吧！",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 128
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人多心，何来得罪之有！鄙人回敬夫人一杯！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 132,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人！今天在下尚未与你祝酒。",
      "tone": "大笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 140,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人酒量真好，不若找一晚让在下陪夫人喝酒，看看谁先醉倒。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 146,
      "line_end": 148
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李先生如此有兴致，赵雅找天在敝府设宴，到时先生莫要推说没空呢！",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "各位须来做见证，看看我们谁先醉倒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 166
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "若定好日子，请通知在下。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "满意吗？",
      "tone": "低语",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 178
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_guo_xiu_er",
      "speaker_name": "郭秀儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "对不起！秀儿有点不舒服，想回房休息。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 180,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ba",
      "speaker_name": "赵霸",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "现在学剑的人，大多急功近利，徒具架势，却没有稳定的身法、马步去配合，对腰力的练习更不看重，有臂力却欠腕力，茫不知腰、臂、腕和步法四方面相辅相成，才能发挥剑法的精华，可知气力的运用乃首要的条件。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 196
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ba",
      "text": "我看空有力气仍没有用，否则嚣魏牟就不会给项少龙宰掉。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 198,
      "line_end": 200
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "只可惜他溜到秦国去，否则定要试试他的剑法厉害至何等程度。",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 206,
      "line_end": 208
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "异日攻入咸阳，不是有机会吗？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 210,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ba",
      "speaker_name": "赵霸",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "李先生以剑法称雄楚国，不知可否找天到敝馆一行？好让赵某大开眼界。",
      "tone": "沉声",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ba",
      "text": "在下每到一地，均爱找当地最著名的剑手切磋比试，赵馆主有此提议，李园实是正中下怀。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_le_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "乐乘",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ba",
      "text": "李先生如此豪气干云，馆主请定下日子、时间，好让我们欣赏到李先生的绝世剑术。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ba",
      "speaker_name": "赵霸",
      "listener": "char_li_yuan",
      "text": "赵某颇有点迫不及待，不若就明天吧！看李先生哪个时间最适合？",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 224,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_yuan",
      "speaker_name": "李园",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ba",
      "text": "明天可不行，皆因在下约了嫣然小姐共游邯郸，不如改在后天午后时分如何？",
      "tone": "得意",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "让本侯陪夫人回府。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 242
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_ya",
      "speaker_name": "赵雅",
      "listener": "char_han_chuang",
      "text": "平山侯的好意心领了，赵雅的脑袋有些昏沉，想独自一人静静。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 244,
      "line_end": 246
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_han_chuang",
      "speaker_name": "韩闯",
      "listener": "char_zhao_ya",
      "text": "夫人爱怎样便怎样吧！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "一起走吧！我却是谈兴正隆，谁愿陪我同车。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "横竖我是一个人来，由鄙人陪侯爷吧！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "想不到先生词锋如此凌厉，连一向能言善辩的李园亦招架不来。只不知你有没有把握战胜他手中之剑，据悉此人确有真才实学。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 260,
      "line_end": 263
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "speaker_name": "项少龙",
      "listener": "char_zhao_mu",
      "text": "有没有把握还是其次的问题，不过武场切磋，用的既是钝口的木剑，又非生死相搏……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 266,
      "line_end": 266
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_zhao_mu",
      "speaker_name": "赵穆",
      "listener": "char_xiang_shao_long",
      "text": "我只是想挫他的气焰，并非要当众杀他。这小子实在太可恨了，若给我把他拿着，定要操他个生不如死。",
      "tone": "愤怒",
      "chapter": 72,
      "line_start": 268,
      "line_end": 271
    }
  ],
